Useful scripts for using/interacting with Appion

============

make_uploader_file.py - create text file containing tilt micrograph pairs for appion
--> RCT_upload.txt - example output from make_uploader_file.py
bbox.csh - box out all .box/.mrc files using batchboxer
boxem.csh - automatically open EMAN's boxer program for all .mrc files within current working directory  
convert_dm3_tif.py - convert .dm3 images into .tif images
